'''Zornak's spaceship''' was the [[Starship/Legends|vessel]] in which [[Zornak]] and his crew traveled to the forest [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Endor/Legends|Endor]]. It had many advanced technological features, including a [[transport chamber]].<ref name="EW14">[[Ewoks (1985) 14|''Ewoks'' (1985) 14]]</ref>

